quran[135]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,"Ta, Ha."
  20,2,"Shikhwakhwishilia Ikurani mbu khonyoole obutinyu tawe."
  20,3,"Halali ibe ametsulisio khu ulia wihotselesinjia."
  20,4,"Naameshio karulanga khu ulia owalonga liloba nende amakulu kali hekulu muno."
  20,5,"Omunji wetsimbabaasi, yachingukha ekulu weshisala shia obwami."
  20,6,"Nebibie ebili mwikulu nende mushialo, nende bili hakari wabio nende ebili hasi weliloba."
  20,7,"Ne kata nolomaloma likhuwa khumwoyo kwa ekulu (nohomba kwa asi), toto ye yamanya akefisa nende kata akali mubwifise muno."
  20,8,"Nyasaye, abulaho nyasaye wundi halali Ye tawe, ne ali nende ameera amalayi muno."
  20,9,"Ne koo, lwakhuulila olukano lwa Musa?"
  20,10,"Olwa yalola omulilo, mana naboolela Abandu bebe mbu: “Linde mbeli, esie toto endutsi omulilo. Ndakhaba endio ndabarerera eshichenga shiomulilo oko, nohomba enyala okhunyoola khumulilo oko obulunjifu.”"
  20,11,"Olwa yakuulakhwo, yalaangwa: “Ewe Musa."
  20,12,"Toto esie nesie Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, kho rusia ebilaro bibio. Toto ewe oli mulitwoma lioluyali elia Tuwa."
  20,13,"Ne esie ekhwaule, kho wulila akofimbulilungwa."
  20,14,"Toto esie nesie Nyasaye, abulaho nyasaye wundi owulali esie tawe, kho laama esie, ne olumilile okhuswaliya khulwokhunzitsulila."
  20,15,"Toto Indukho itsia okhuula, ndenya okhuyifisa katong’ane, kho buli omundu arungwe khukalia akayakholanga."
  20,16,"Kho, toto balakhwikalila okhuisuubila balia abalaisuubilanga tawe, abaloondanga butswa obwikombi bwa emioyo chiabu abeene; wakhetsa wasikha."
  20,17,"Ne nishina esho shili mumukhono kukwo omulunji ewe Musa?”"
  20,18,"Naboola Mbu: “Ino ni indabushi yanje yandisililangakhwo, ne eyikwisilinjia amasafu ke ebiayo bianje, ne khandi echikhonyelanga khumilimo chindi.”"
  20,19,"Nyasaye naboola mbu: “Isukune hasi ewe Musa.”"
  20,20,"Mana nachisukuna, lola, niikalukhana inzukha imoolanga tsimbilo."
  20,21,"Nyasaye naboola mbu; “Ibukule, ne olaria tawe, khulayikalusia shingala ibeele anyuma awo."
  20,22,"Ne ra omukhono kukwo mukwaya, kularula nikuli omulafu tswe, kubula obubii bwosibwosi. Shino ni eshimanyisio shindi."
  20,23,"Kho khukhwechesie mubimanyisio biefu ebikhongo."
  20,24,"Tsia khu Firaun, toto ye yabura eshichelo.”"
  20,25,"Naboola mbu: “Ewe Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, mbangulila eshilifu shianje."
  20,26,"Ne khola amakhuwa kanje kabe amaangu."
  20,27,"Ne rusiliakhowo eshilimi khululimi lwanje."
  20,28,"Banyoole akhuwulila amakhuwa kanje."
  20,29,"Ne umberesie omukhoonyi okhurula mubandu banje."
  20,30,"Omusiani wefu Haruni."
  20,31,"Undemo amaani okhumwikhonyela ye."
  20,32,"Ne mure halala ninasi khumilimo chianje chino."
  20,33,"Kho khunyoole okhukhutswenula muno."
  20,34,"Ne khukhurumbule mubunji."
  20,35,"Toto ewe okhulolanga obulayi muno.”"
  20,36,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu: “Toto ofuchililwe amasayo koko ewe Musa."
  20,37,"Ne toto khwamalakho okhukhukholela obulayi olundi."
  20,38,"Olwa khwafimbulila mama wuwo kalia akakhwamufimbulila."
  20,39,"Mbu mure mwisanduku mana olire mumwalo, mana omwalo oko kulamusukuna khulukuku anyoole okhubukulwa nende omusuku wanje khandi omusuku wuwe, ne ndakhurakhwo obuyanzi okhurula khwisie, ne mbu olelwe mutsimoni tsianje."
  20,40,"Olwa omukhana wenyu yachendanga naboola mbu: 'Koo, ebechesiekhwo Omundu unyala okhumulela?' Mana nikhukhukalusia khu mama wuwo kho tsimoni tsisie tsisangale, ne kho alabeelela tawe. Ne wera Omundu mana nikhukhuhabina okhurula mushibeela eshikhongo esho, mana nikhukhutema amatemo amanji. Mana niwikhala emika eminji halala nende Abandu ba Madyan, mana khandi witsile shingala walachilwa ewe Musa."
  20,41,"Ne ekhuloboole khulwa esie omwene."
  20,42,"Tsia ewe nende omusiani wenyu halala nende ebifune bianje, ne mulachonya okhunzitsulila tawe."
  20,43,"Tsie khu Firauni, toto ye yabura eshichelo."
  20,44,"Mumuboolele amakhuwa amaangu, yakhaaba ario yetsulila (amachelo) nohomba yaria Nyasaye."""
  20,45,"Nibaboola mbu: “Ewe Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, efwe toto khuritsanga mbu anyala okhukhuleka efwe nohomba okhuburirila eshichero.”"
  20,46,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “Mularia tawe. Toto esie endi halala ninanyu. Ewulilanga, ne endolanga."
  20,47,"Tsie mana mumuboolele mbu: 'Toto efwe khuli Abarumwa ba Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Kho balekhule Abaana ba Israili barule halala ninafu ne olabara mushinyaasio tawe. Toto khukhwitsile nende ebimanyisio birula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Ne omulembe kulaba khubalia baloondanga obulunjifu."
  20,48,"Toto efwe khurererwe obufimbuli mbu eshinyasio shilanyoola balia abayingananga mana bafutare omukongo.'”"
  20,49,"(Firauni) Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi ni wina, ewe Musa?”"
  20,50,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi ni ulia wahelesia buli eshindu imero yashio mana nashilunjisia.”"
  20,51,"Naboola mbu: “Ne babura khale balia baliba barie?”"
  20,52,"Naboola mbu: “Obumanyi bwako buli khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi mushitabu. Nyasaye wanje Omulesi shakoranga nohomba shiyebililanga tawe."
  20,53,"Ulia wabakholela liloba okhuba obulili, ne nabarereramwo tsinjila, mana niyeshia amatsi okhurula mwikulu, ni khu ako nikhumesiliakhwo emimela chiaukhaane."""
  20,54,"Lie, ne mulisie ebiayo bienyu. Toto mukano bilimwo ebimanyisio khubandu bamachesi."
  20,55,"Okhurula khulio (liloba) khwabaloonga, ne khulibakalusia mulio, ne mulio khulibarusia khandi (mube abalamu)."
  20,56,"Ne toto khwamwechesia ebimanyisio biefu bioosi, halali yayingana nakhaya."
  20,57,"Naboola mbu: “Witsile okhukhurusia efwe khushialo shiefu khubulosi bubwo, ewe Musa?"
  20,58,"Mana efwe khwitsa okhukhurerera obulosi shinga obo. Kho, raho hakari wefu ninawe ebise biokhubukanana, ebia khulafunaka efwe nohomba ewe tawe. Abe habundu halayi muno.”"
  20,59,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Ebise bienyu ni inyanga yoburone. Ne Abandu bakhung’asibwe itsuli.”"
  20,60,"Mana Firauni nakalukha inyuma, mana nakhung’asia ebifwanga biayee, mana niyetsa."
  20,61,"Musa nababoolela mbu: “Abaane enywee! Mulachishila Nyasaye obubeyi tawe, yakhetsa yabamala nende eshinyasio. Ne toto yamala okhubiyilwa ulia uchikhanga.”"
  20,62,"Kho mana nibasolana abeene khubeene khulwa likhuwa liabu elo, mana nibasanjilana mubwifisi."
  20,63,"Nibaboola mbu: “Toto Abandu bano ni abalosi babili, benyanga okhubarusia mushialo shienyu khubulosi bwabu, ne bainieho injila yenyu yobulamu indayi po."
  20,64,"Kho lano khung’asie halala ebifwanga bienyu bioosi, mana mwitse nimuli khulunyaali. Ne toto Inyanga yino ulashila niye witsa okhuba hekulu."""
  20,65,"Nibaboola mbu: “Ewe Musa, ewe newe ularanjilila okhusukuna nohomba efwe khuranjilile?”"
  20,66,"Naboola mbu: “Enywe ranjilile okhusukuna.” Lola! Emikoye chiabu nende tsindabushi tsiabu nitsimuloloshela khulwa obulosi bwabu mbu tsimoolanga tsimbilo."
  20,67,"Mana Musa niyenjilwamwo oburi mumwoyo kukwe."
  20,68,"Nikhuboola mbu: “Olaria tawe. Toto ewe newe witsa okhushila."
  20,69,"Kho sukuna shili mumukhono kukwo omusatsa, shitsa okhumila biabakasiyie ebo. Toto bakasiye butswa ebifwanga biobulosi, ne Omulosi shashirangakhwo wosiwosi watsila tawe.”"
  20,70,"Mana abalosi abo boosi nibakwa hasi nibasujuda. Nibaboola mbu: “Khusuubile Nyasaye wa Haruni nende Musa.”"
  20,71,"(Firauni) Naboola mbu: “Ehh! Mumusuubile neeshili okhubasubula. Toto ye (Musa) niye omukhongo wenyu owabechesia obulosi. Kholano toto nditsa okhubateta emikhono chienyu nende amakulu kenyu buchikha, ne toto nditsa okhubabaamba khumisala chietsitende, ne toto mulamanya mbu niwina mwifwe omululu muno weshinyasio, khandi wookhushitsililisia muno."""
  20,72,"Nibaboola mbu: “Shikhulakhwaula ewe okhushila ebimanyisio bili habulafu bikhwitsile tawe, khandi okhushila ulia wakhuloonga. Kho, khalaka eshiina shiosishiosi shionyala okhukhalaka. Ewe onyala okhukhalaka eshina shilondokhana nende obulamu bwokhushialo khuno butswa."
  20,73,"Toto efwe khusuubile Nyasaye wefu Omulesi; kho akhuleshele ebionono biefu nende akokhunichilisiye kano akobulosi. Ne Nyasaye nomulayi, khandi niwokhubaho tsinyanga tsioosi.”"
  20,74,"Toto ulia ulitsa khu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, nali mbu niwamabii, toto alinyoola omulilo kwa Jahanamu, shalifwamwo tawe ne shalimenyamwo (obulamu obulayi) tawe."
  20,75,"Ne ulia ulimwitsila nali omusubili owakhola ebikhole ebilayi, abo nibo balinyoola ebisaala bia hekulu."
  20,76,"Emikunda chilaliwa tawe, chiburangamwo emialo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi. Ne oko niko omurungo kwa buli ulia wetswenula."
  20,77,"Ne toto khwafimbulila Musa mbu: “Orule nende Abasumba banje, ne obakholele Injila yokhulukongo inyumu munyanza. Olaria okhunyoolwa nohomba olaria shiosishiosi tawe.”"
  20,78,"Firauni nabalondakhwo halala nende omukanda kukwe kwabalwani, mana nikabanyoola munyanza omo akabanyoola."
  20,79,"Mana Firaun nakosia Abandu baye, ne shiyabalunjisia tawe."
  20,80,"""Enywe Abana ba Israil, toto efwe khwabahabina okhurulana nende abasuku benyu, mana nikhubalaka mbu mwitse ebuleka womukhono musatsa weshikulu shia Tur, mana nikhubeshilia Manna nende Salwa."
  20,81,"Lie mubilayi bilia ebiakhubakabile, ne mularuuma olwakho khu ako tawe, liruma lianje liakhetsa liabatila. Ne ulia weliruma lianje linyoola alaba amalile okhusikha."
  20,82,"Ne toto esie endi wokhuleshela muno khu ulia owusaba eshileshelo, nasuubila, nakhola amalayi mana natila obulunjifu."
  20,83,"Ne nishina shiakhuyungubasia nolekha Abandu bobo ewe Musa?"""
  20,84,"Naboola mbu: ”Bali inyuma wanje banondangakhwo. Ne ekholele lwangu okhukhwitsila Nyasaye wanje Omulesi kho onyoole okhumba obuchami (bwo)."""
  20,85,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu: “Toto Khuhelesiye Abandu bao amatemo ewe niwakharula, ne Omusamaria abakosiyie.”"
  20,86,"Mana Musa nakalukha khubandu bebe nasinyishe nabeelele muno. Naboola mbu: “Enywe abandu banje, Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi shiyabalakakhwo indache indayi? Koo, ebise ebo bimurambiyile ebia indache eyo nohomba mwenyele mbu liruma okhurula khu Nyasaye wenyu omulesi libeshele, khulwendio mufunache indache yanje?”"
  20,87,"Nibaboola mbu: “Efwe shikhufunache indache yiyio khukhwenya khwefu tawe, halali efwe khwatukhwa emisiko chiebirone biabandu mana nikhuchisukuna (mumulilo, nichisalulukha nichikasia eshifwanani shia Nyasaye). Ne endiosa nilwa Omusamaria yasukuna yesi.”"
  20,88,"Mana nabakasiliamwo eshimosi shilikho eshikhuli shirusinjia oluyoka. Mana nibaboola mbu; “Uno niye nyasaye wenyu khandi niye nyasaye wa Musa, halali (Musa) yebilila.”"
  20,89,"Koo, shibalolakhwo mbu (eshimosi esho) sishibakalusinjia likhuwa tawe, nohomba sishiakhabakhola libii liosiliosi tawe nohomba okhubakhoonya?"
  20,90,"Ne Haruni yababoolela khale awo mbu; “Enywe Abandu banje, toto enywe mutemelwe sa nende kano. Ne toto Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi ni ulia owetsimbabaasi tsinyinji muno. Kho munoonde, ne muwulile amakhuwa kanje.”"
  20,91,"Nibaboola mbu; “Shikhulalekha okhushilaama tawe okhula shingala Musa alachelela.”"
  20,92,"(Olwa Musa yachelela) Yaboola mbu: “Ewe Haruni, nishina shikhukayile shingala obalutsi nibakorere?"
  20,93,"Okhunoondakho? Nohomba olobele likhuwa lianje?”"
  20,94,"(Haruni) Naboola mbu: “Ewe Omwana wa mama wanje, olakhwesa tsindefu nohomba omurwe kwanje tawe. Toto esie ndaria mbu oletsa waboola mbu okabule Abana ba Israil, ne showulile likhuwa lianje tawe.”"
  20,95,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Ewe Omusamaria, obele orie okhukhola kano?”"
  20,96,"Naboola mbu: “Endutsi kabalalolanga tawe, mana nendila ebuleka inditi wa amalaro akomurumwa ulia yasena. Mana nesukuna. Ne endio nilwa omwoyo kwanje kwambila.”"
  20,97,"(Musa) naboola mbu; “Mana rula tsia! Ne toto kalaba khwiwe mubulamu bwao bwokhushialo okhuboola mbu: 'Olandilakhwo tawe.' Ne toto oli nende indakano yolalifunachilwa tawe. Ne khahengakhwo Nyasaye wuwo owotsililile okhumulaama. Toto khwitsa okhumusamba mana khumutumulile munyanza akoreremwo."""
  20,98,"Toto Nyasaye wenyu ni Allah (Nyasaye), ulia uli mbu abulaho ulaamungwa khubwatoto halali Ye tawe. Yaswania buli eshindu obumanyi."
  20,99,"Ne endio nilwakhukhukanilanga khumakhuwa kali imbeli wuwo. Ne toto khwakhuhelesia ametsulilo okhurula khwifwe."
  20,100,"Balia betsa okhuba ehale ninako, toto abo balichinga inyanga yeyindukho emisiko."
  20,101,"Balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi, ne ni obubii buli burie khumundu inyanga yeyindukho okhuchinga emisiko echo."
  20,102,"Inyanga yabilifurwa mulwika, ne khulikhung’asia aboononi inyanga eyo, tsimoni tsiabu nitsili bulu (khulwa oburii)."
  20,103,"Balimonyaniamwo abeene khubeene, ne baliboola mbu: “Shimwekhala khushialo halali tsinyanga ekhumi butswa.”"
  20,104,"Efwe khumanyile muno akabaliboola, olwa abalayi muno mubo khunjila baliboola mbu: “Enywe shimwekhalamwo halali inyanga ndala yonyene.”"
  20,105,"Ne bakhurebanga amakhuwa ketsingulu, boola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi alitsisia masia."
  20,106,"Ne alitsilekha shinga eshikuri."
  20,107,"Sholilolamwo lituoma nohomba eshitulo tawe."
  20,108,"Inyanga eyo balilonda khumulanji owa yesiyesi shalinyala okhumukorakhwo tawe, ne emioyo chiliihotselesilia Omunji wetsimbabaasi, ne sholiwulila halali tsimbindo tsiebilenje nende okhwimonyelesia."
  20,109,"Inyanga eyo khulibulaho okhusabilwa khwosikhwosi halali khu ulia wachamilwa nende Omunji wetsimbabaasi, mana afuchilile likhuwa lilie."
  20,110,"Yamanya akali imbeli nende akali inyuma wabu. Nabo shibanyala okhumumanya obulayi muno tawe."
  20,111,"Ne obweni bulitutuyila Omulamu Ulafwitsanga tawe. Ne toto baliba nibabiyilwe boosi balia bachinga obubii."
  20,112,"Ne ulia ukhola amalayi niyasuubila, shaliria okhukholelwa obubii nohomba okhwimwa eshishie tawe."
  20,113,"Ne endio nilwakhweshia Ikurani mulwarabu, ne nikhwinoosiamwo amekanyilisio ketsimbia tsioosi khobanyoole okhuria nende okhwilinda, ne ibarerere ametsulisio."
  20,114,"Ne toto Nyasaye niwoluyali, owahekulu, Omwami watoto. Ne olayuyukhanila (okhusoma) Ikurani obufimbuli bwayio nibushili okhuwa tawe. Ne boola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi meeta obumanyi.”"
  20,115,"Ne toto khwalaka Adam khale indache, mana niyebilila, ne shikhwalola khuye lichomo likhongo tawe."
  20,116,"Ne olwa khwaboolela Abamalaika mbu: “Rerere Adam obweni hasi.” Boosi nibara obweni hasi halali Ibilisi, yaloba."
  20,117,"Ne nikhuboola mbu: “Ewe Adam, toto uno ni omusuku wuwo nende womukhasi wuwo, kho alabayinia mumukunda kwomwikulu tawe; mwaba khubutinyu."
  20,118,"Toto ewe sholawulilamwo inzala tawe nohomba okhuba eshiekenyi tawe."
  20,119,"Ne toto ewe sholiwulilamwo obulo nohomba oluuya tawe."""
  20,120,"Mana Shetani namubeyiabeyiamwo, namuboolela mbu: “Ewe Adam, ekhumanyiekhwo omusala kwokhumenya tsinyanga tsioosi nende obwami bulawa tawe?”"
  20,121,"Mana nibalia khumusaala oko, mana eshiekenyi shiabu nishibaloleshela. Nibachaka okhwifimba amasafu komumukunda kwomwikulu oko. Mana Adam nakosela Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, nakora injila."
  20,122,"Mana Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi namwawula, namuhelesia eshileshelo, ne namulunjisia."
  20,123,"Naboola mbu: “Yishe okhurulamwo mwesi nimuli abasuku abeene khubeene. Ne obulunjifu okhurula khwisie nibuboolela, ulia ulalonda obulunjifu bwanje obo shalikora nohomba shalisanda tawe."
  20,124,"Ne ulia ura emukongo obwitsulisio bwanje, alaba nende eshimenyo shiobusandi, ne inyanga yeyindukho alikhung’asibwa nali omuwofu."
  20,125,"Aliboola mbu: 'Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, khulwashina niwukhung’asia nendi omuwofu, ne ndali nendolanga obulayi muno?'”"
  20,126,"Alimuboolela mbu: “Endio nilwa biakhwitsila ebimanyisio biefu nawe nobibilila, kho kata wesi inyanga yino wibililwe.”"
  20,127,"Ne endio nilwa khurunganga ulia waburirisia eshichelo, ne nalasuubila ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi tawe, ne eshinyasio shiomwikulu neshilulu muno khandi eshiokhutong’a muno."
  20,128,"Bishili okhubabela habulafu emikanda chinga chia khwasishia echibachendanga mutsingo tsiabu. Toto mwako bilimwo ebimanyisio khubandu bamachesi."
  20,129,"Ne likhayanga okhuba likhuwa liaranjilila okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nende ebise biarebwaho, toto eshinyasio shiakhoolele (shiokhusishia aboononi abo)."
  20,130,"Kho, wisumilisie khukababoolanga, ne tswenula Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khuluyali lulwe eliuba nilishili okhurula nende nilishili okhukwa, nende ebise bieshilo biosi omutswenule nende hakari weshitere; wakhaba orio khowanyoola akakhuchamisia."
  20,131,"Ne olakhondiola tsimoni tsitsio khubwokholo bwa khwakholela abaandi mubo tawe; oburone bwobulamu bwokhushialo, kho khunyoole okhubatemamwo. Ne omukabo kwa Nyasaye wuwo omulesi ni omulayi khandi nookutong’anga muno."
  20,132,"Ne lomesia abandu bobo okhulumilila okhulaama Iswala, ne witinyilisie omwene khuyo. Shikhukhusabanga omukabo kwosikwosi tawe, nefwe khukhukabilanga. Ne omumalilikho omulayi ni kwokhuba noburi khu Nyasaye."
  20,133,"Ne baboola mbu: “Shichila shina nalakhwitsila nende eshimanyisio okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi tawe?” Koo, shibiabetselakhwo ebimanyisio ebia habulafu ebili mubitabu biakhale tawe?"
  20,134,"Ne bibetsanga mbu toto khwabasishia khushinyasio Omurumwa oyo nashili okhwitsa, bakhaboolele mbu: “Ewe Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, shichila shina nolakhurerera Omurumwa, khwaloonda ebimanyisio bibio nikhushili okhututuyibwa endi, nende okhunyoola tsisoni tawe?”"
  20,135,"Boola mbu: “Buli mulala alindanga (omurungo kukwe). Kho, nakhalinde. Muletsa okhumanya ahambi hano mbu ni babu wina abali khunjila ya habwene, ne babu wina balunjikha.”"
